OK, I got this issue And I am working on making weex support 64-bit cpu, I think you may fix your problem through this way temporarilly.

`Remove all your app's 64-bit so file, And load 32-bit so file in all devices.`

```gradle
android {
    ...
    defaultConfig {
        ...
        ndk {
            abiFilters "armeabi-v7a", "x86"
        }

        packagingOptions {
            exclude "lib/arm64-v8a/xxx.so"
        }
    }
}
```

