@vikasrathore  
maybe found the tmp soultion on [google's doc](https://codelabs.developers.google.com/codelabs/your-first-dynamic-app/index.html#3)
open app/build.gradle and add the following inside the android {} block:
```
bundle {
   language {
       enableSplit = true
   }
   density {
       enableSplit = true
   }
   abi {
       enableSplit = true
     //change to false
   }
}
```

if still not work , wait 64bit support （will be completed at the middle of June.）
 check process on [dev mail list ](https://lists.apache.org/thread.html/bc2be5495bfe47df0fcbfcbf16299023e24a7ec8e254120e60d553ec@%3Cdev.weex.apache.org%3E)

and this issue will be closed ， all 64bit issue be merged to #2389
